{
  "texts": [
    "How can these frameworks be adapted to address the emerging challenges (e.g., lack of explainability of black-boxed foundation models)?",
    "This article has elucidated the emergence of foundation models as a transformative paradigm for AI.",
    "Foundation models promise unprecedented opportunities to advance the performance and accessibility of AI applications across various sectors and represent a significant shift in how near-future AI systems will be developed, deployed, and used.",
    "We delineated key features of foundation models such as emergent capabilities, homogenization, and prompt sensitivity.",
    "These features redefine the stakeholders and dynamics of the AI ecosystem, including a pull toward a centralization of power and the rise of regulatory challenges through the diffusion of accountability and control."
  ]
}